premise_source_doc_sentence: Victor Marie Hugo  (  -LSB- viktɔʁ maʁi yɡo -RSB- ; 26 February 1802 -- 22 May 1885  )  was a French poet , novelist , and dramatist of the Romantic movement .
Victor Hugo  (  1802 -- 1885  )  was a French poet , novelist , and dramatist of the Romantic , author of Les Misérables .
